Set up instructions to get it running

1. install xampp 
2. copy the folder (school_management_system) into htdoc folder inside xampp installation folder
    PATH: Windows - C:/xampp/htdocs  linux - /opt/lampp/htdocs

3. open the xampp control panel and start the apache and the mysql

4. open the url localhost/phpmyadmin in your web browser and import the database in this folder (/school_management_system/Database) into phpmyadmin

5. make sure the database name is 'school_management_system_DB'

6. Enter the url localhost/school_management_system in your browser

